# parallel-agent-myrmidon-swarm-orchestration — History

## v1.1.0 (2026-06-13)

**Changed by:** SHA-pin swarm session 2026-06-13 (13-repo parallel dispatch)
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed
- Added Failed Attempt #20: Haiku agents ignore provided canonical SHA maps and query their own
- Added Failed Attempt #21: BLOCKED mergeStateStatus misinterpreted as failure
- Added 13-repo SHA-pin swarm 2026-06-13 to Verified Swarm Configurations table

### Why
13-repo parallel SHA-pin swarm revealed that Haiku agents will override canonical SHA maps with their own API lookups, producing wrong version SHAs. Also clarified that GitHub's BLOCKED merge state = CI pending, not failure.

